N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 75.3 - Examination in speech-language pathology

State Regulations

The department may accept grades satisfactory to the State

Board for Speech-Language Pathology and Audiology on an examination determined
by the department to be acceptable for licensure as a speech-language
pathologist. Notes
